										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>相信很多朋友都跟小编一样，一到夏天就心烦气躁，食欲全无。这个时候，只有清甜鲜亮的水果才能够激起人的食欲：凉爽的西瓜，香甜的荔枝、甜脆的桃子……水果捞、水果船、水果沙拉，不仅味道好，同时还能补充各种营养和维生素，简直没人能拒绝！</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-294 aligncenter" title="a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921.jpg" alt="a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921" width="1055" height="693" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921.jpg 1055w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921-300x197.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921-1024x673.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a54b858111624801a2c6711c62cb3921-768x504.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1055px) 100vw, 1055px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>但是你知道吗，水果虽好，但是也是有讲究的，要根据自己的体质和实际情况来，否则可能会适得其反哦！</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-295 aligncenter" title="e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922.jpg" alt="e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922" width="1128" height="691" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922.jpg 1128w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922-300x184.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922-1024x627.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/e745645fd4c1431f95d7f7725ab32922-768x470.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1128px) 100vw, 1128px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>寒性水果：</p>
<p>夏天的水果多属于寒凉性的，如：梨、苹果、香瓜、西瓜、梨、香蕉、奇异果、芒果、柿子、荸荠、甜瓜、柚子等。</p>
<p>实热体质的人夏天代谢旺盛，交感神经占优势，出汗多，经常脸色通红、口干舌燥、易烦躁、容易便秘，适宜食用此类寒凉水果。但是对于气虚、脾虚，或是肠胃功能不好的老人和孩子来说，不太适合吃寒凉水果，如果真的很想吃，可以在午饭后、晚饭前，少吃一点，不可过量。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-296 aligncenter" title="1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602.jpg" alt="1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602" width="1102" height="694" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602.jpg 1102w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602-1024x645.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1d3dac94f57543dea17903c3cce99602-768x484.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1102px) 100vw, 1102px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>温热水果：</p>
<p>众多水果中，荔枝、桂圆、杏等属于温热性也是相当受人们欢迎的。尤其对于虚寒体质的人来说，他们气虚脾虚，基础代谢率低，体内产生的热量少，四肢即便在夏天也是冷的，最适合吃一些温热的水果。不过，正在发烧或某器官正在发炎的人尽量避免食用温热水果。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-297 aligncenter" title="553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c.jpg" alt="553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c" width="983" height="658" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c.jpg 983w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c-300x201.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/553d9fd7db0245229ea606baa93def1c-768x514.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 983px) 100vw, 983px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>不仅如此，以下几种夏天常吃的水果，也要注意，一不小心就吃多了，很可能会造成身体不适。</p>
<p>荔枝</p>
<p>时下正是荔枝大量上市的季节，但要注意的是，鲜荔枝本身含糖量很高。吃多了不仅容易导致肥胖，如果连续且大量地进食荔枝，容易导致牙痛、咽喉疼痛，孩子尤其要注意。</p>
<p>健康吃法：每次量不超过一个拳头大小</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-298 aligncenter" title="17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494.jpg" alt="17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494" width="1043" height="682" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494.jpg 1043w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494-300x196.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494-1024x670.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/17b326a66a054a42beb68b6aed018494-768x502.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1043px) 100vw, 1043px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>桃子</p>
<p>桃子纤维能预防便秘，同时也是补气养血的佳果。虽然民间有“桃养人”的说法，但桃子不能一次吃太多。桃子中含有大量膳食纤维，尤其是硬桃，吃多了可能引发消化系统功能紊乱，出现腹胀、腹痛等不适症状。</p>
<p>健康吃法：一天别超过两个。吃桃前可用盐直接搓桃皮，能较干净地去除桃毛。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-299 aligncenter" title="1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96.jpg" alt="1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96" width="949" height="673" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96.jpg 949w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96-300x213.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1b8139366f6943c29eaa6eae4b1e1d96-768x545.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 949px) 100vw, 949px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>榴莲</p>
<p>榴莲被誉为 “水果之王”，营养丰富，但也并非人人适宜，尤其是阴虚体质的人群不宜多吃。榴莲中脂肪含量为4.1%，是所有水果中含量最高的，且榴莲性热，如果吃过多的话容易导致脸上的痤疮加剧，而且会有口干舌燥的感觉。甚至有的时候，还会引发流鼻血的情况。</p>
<p>健康吃法：配着山竹一起吃，这是因为山竹性偏寒凉可以清热“败火”</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-300 aligncenter" title="a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1.jpg" alt="a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1" width="973" height="667" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1.jpg 973w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1-300x206.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a73b46aa657e42d6820fc313fd5802a1-768x526.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 973px) 100vw, 973px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>当然了，大家在吃水果的时候，也不要贪食，注意食用量，《中国居民膳食指南(2016版)》建议每人每天摄入200~350克新鲜水果，也就是半斤上下。一个三口之家，一周采购4~5千克的水果就可以了哦，千万别贪食。饭后立即吃水果，不但不会助消化，反而会造成胀气和便秘。因此，吃水果宜在饭后2小时或饭前1小时。只有在正确的时间，吃合适的水果，才能健康又养颜。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-301 aligncenter" title="4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2.jpg" alt="4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2" width="1026" height="744" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2.jpg 1026w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2-300x218.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2-1024x743.jpg 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4fe7652f6d7844bbb1d1a28a3cd316f2-768x557.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1026px) 100vw, 1026px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p>怎么样，关于怎样吃水果的小知识，大家都掌握了吗？日常会分享改革中饮食小知识和美食，千万不要错过哦！</p>
